{"lemma":"عِناقِ","slug":"عِناقِ","root":"ع.ن.ق","root_slug":"ع-ن-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ن-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30792"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَانَقَ (ʕānaqa) (form III)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hugging, embracement","examples":[{"text":"وَإِنْ نَقَعَ ٱلصَّرِيخُ إِلَى مَكَانٍ / نَصَبْنَ لَهُ مُؤَلَّلَةً دِقَاقَا / فَكَانَ ٱلطَّعْنُ بَيْنَهُمَا جَوَابًا / وَكَانَ ٱللَّبْثُ بَيْنَهُمَا فُوَاقَا / مُلَاقِيَةً نَوَاصِيهَا ٱلْمَنَايَا / مُعَوَّدَةً فَوَارِسُهَا ٱلْعِنَاقَا"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"young goat, kid that has not passed a year"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕi.naːq/","/ʕa.naːq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30792","headword_ar":"عَنَاقٌ","root":"Enq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-kid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when a year old,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not yet a year old:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, Msb, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a lamb"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is just born;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saxolapN","text_ar":"سَخْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEonaAqN","text_ar":"مِعْنَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence:]) pl. (of pauc., TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEonuqN","text_ar":"اَعْنُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (of mult., TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EunuwqN","text_ar":"عُنُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K, TA) and also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EunuqN","text_ar":"عُنُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with two dammehs. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEunuwqu baEoda Aln~uwqi","text_ar":"العُنُوقُ بَعْدَ النُّوقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-kids after the she-camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (T, O, K, &c.,) meaning he has become a pastor of she-kids after having been a pastor of she-camels, (T,) is a prov., (T, O, K, &c.,) applied to him who has become lowered from a high station, (T,) or to a case of straitness after ampleness. (O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEanaAqu","text_ar":"العَنَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanaAqu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"عَنَاقُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Mgh, O, Msb, K, TA, &c.,) [which latter is now applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The badger; ursus meles;"},{"kind":"text","text":"if correctly, app. because it burrows in the earth; but this application does not well agree with the following descriptions;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain beast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the beasts of the earth, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahod","text_ar":"فَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lynx"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"about the size of the dog, an animal of prey,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that hunts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smaller than the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahod","text_ar":"فَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long in the back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~ufahu","text_ar":"التُّفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or, by some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~uf~apu","text_ar":"النُّفَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, * Msb,) with teshdeed to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":"and with the fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfunojulu","text_ar":"الفُنْجُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siyaAh kuw$","text_ar":"سِيَاه كُوش"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siyaAh Guw$","text_ar":"سِيَاه گُوش"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. “ black ear, ” if meaning the badger, app. because of the black mark on each ear]; (Mgh, O, K, TA;) said by IAmb to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a foul beast, that is not eaten, and that does not eat anything but flesh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) Az says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is above the size of the Chinese dog, hunts like as does the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahod","text_ar":"فَهْد"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eats flesh, and is of the beasts of prey; and is said to be the only beast that conceals its footmarks when it runs, except the hare;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and he says also, “ I have seen it in the desert ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaAdiyap","text_ar":"البَادِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and it was"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"black in the head, the rest of it being white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"” the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EunuwqN","text_ar":"عُنُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEanaAqu","text_ar":"العَنَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also the name of (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The middle star"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ζ","text_ar":"ζ","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the three stars called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAt naEo$ AlkuboraY","text_ar":"بَنَات نَعْش الكُبْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the tail of Ursa Major"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, * K, * TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by it is a small star called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~uhaA","text_ar":"السُّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by looking at which persons try their powers of sight."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kzw. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaAy^idu","text_ar":"القَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qwd","text_ar":"قود"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b4-  [And the same, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanaAqu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"عَنَاقُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is the name of (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star g in what is figured by some as the right, and by others as the left, leg,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foot, of Andromeda."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanaAqN","text_ar":"عَنَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEanoqaA='u","text_ar":"العَنْقَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEonaqu","text_ar":"اَعْنَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hard affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"event"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiYa minohu A^u*unaYo EanaAqK","text_ar":"لَقِىَ مِنْهُ اُذُنَىْ عَنَاقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, TA, *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanaAqa AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"عَنَاقَ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He experienced, from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hard affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S, O, TA. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^u*unaYo EanaAqK","text_ar":"بِاُذُنَىْ عَنَاقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered an exorbitant lie."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disappointment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, O, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanaAqapN","text_ar":"عَنَاقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) Such is the meaning in the saying of a poet,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ubotumo biAlEanaAqi","text_ar":"اُبْتُمْ بِالعَنَاقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye returned with disappointment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O, TA:) or the meaning is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAlmunokari","text_ar":"بالمُنْكَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with that which was disapproved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; agreeably with an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEanaAqu","text_ar":"العَنَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"by 'Alee Ibn-Hamzeh. (TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stony tract such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~ap","text_ar":"حَرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b8-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poor-rate of two years:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the saying of Aboo-Bekr (K, TA) to 'Omar, when he contended in war with the apostates, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo manaEuwniY EanaAqFA","text_ar":"لَوْ مَنَعُونِى عَنَاقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If they refused me a poor-rate of two years"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but it is also otherwise related, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiqaAlFA","text_ar":"عِقَالًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a poor-rate of a year."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA","IAth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}